{
"cn"
:
"Aider 是由 Aider-AI 团队开源的 AI 编程工具，它以 命令行/终端为主界面，无需复杂图形界面即可与大型语言模型 (LLM) 搭档编程。\n开箱即用地支持 Claude 3.7 Sonnet、DeepSeek R1、Chat V3、OpenAI o1、o3-mini、GPT-4o 等主流模型，还可连接本地或兼容 API 的任意 LLM。它会自动对整个 Git 仓库生成代码结构地图，从而在多个文件间理解上下文并执行连贯修改。Aider 同时支持超过 100 种编程语言，可自动生成语义化的 Git 提交信息并执行提交；支持语音输入（Voice-to-Code）、嵌入截图/网页内容、自动 lint 与测试，适合开发者在本地 workflow 中实现\"AI Pair-Programming\"。\n项目地址: https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider\n"
,
"en"
:
"Aider is an open-source AI coding assistant developed by the Aider-AI team. Designed primarily for the command line or terminal, it enables seamless collaboration with large language models (LLMs) without the need for a complex graphical interface.\nIt supports popular models out of the box, including Claude 3.7 Sonnet, DeepSeek R1, Chat V3, OpenAI o1, o3-mini, and GPT-4o, and can also connect to any local or API-compatible LLM. Aider automatically maps the code structure of your entire Git repository, allowing it to understand context across multiple files and make coherent edits.\nWith support for over 100 programming languages, Aider can automatically generate semantic Git commit messages and perform commits. It also supports voice-to-code input, embedding screenshots or web content, and automatic linting and testing—making it ideal for developers to achieve AI pair programming within their local workflow.\nProject URL: https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider\n"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://aider"
,
"#exec"
:
"xrc aider 2>/dev/null"
}
